🐍 Python Quiz Game 🎮
This is a fun and interactive quiz game designed to test your knowledge of Python programming! Built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, this lightweight web app delivers a smooth and responsive quiz experience right in your browser.

💡 Features
✅ Multiple-choice questions on core Python concepts

⏱️ Timer-based quiz (optional)

🧠 Randomized questions for every playthrough

🌈 Stylish and clean UI using HTML & CSS

📊 Score tracking and instant feedback

🔁 Replay button to retake the quiz anytime

🚀 Technologies Used
HTML – for structuring the quiz layout

CSS – for styling and responsive design

JavaScript – for game logic, question flow, and interaction

